As the dust settles on Rings of Power Season 1... I wanted to examine why the worlds most expensive video series is killing the legacy of its source material in a way very few people could have anticipated. 

Amazon has managed to pollute the lore of this world so badly... it will serve as a barrier to entry for younger generations who otherwise might have enjoyed one of the best fantasy worlds in history.
